- Do not add Tailwind, shadcn, or any pre-built component library.
- Do not add `overflow: hidden` to `html`/`body`.
- Do not disable user zoom in `app.html`.
- Do not hardcode colors in component CSS when a semantic token exists.
- Do not build custom form validation ‚Äî use Superforms + Valibot.
- Do not use plain `<img>` for brand or CMS images without a documented reason.
- Do not add `loading="lazy"` to the page LCP image.
- Do not add a Google Fonts CDN link.
- Do not commit `node_modules/`, `.svelte-kit/`, `build/`, or generated image output directories.
- Do not use `npm`, `npx`, `pnpm`, or `yarn` ‚Äî this project is Bun-only.
- Do not commit `.env` or any file containing real secrets.
- Do not add SQLite ‚Äî Postgres is the runtime data store.
- Do not add n8n as a package dependency ‚Äî it is an external operator, not an app dependency.
- Do not use gray-matter for pure YAML files (`content/pages/`, `content/team/`, `content/testimonials/`).
- Do not rename CMS fields without updating config, content files, types, loaders, components, and docs.
- Do not make webhook calls blocking ‚Äî n8n downtime must not break user-facing forms.
